 "cells": [
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "# Sales Analysis Dashboard - EDA 📊\n",
    "\n",
    "## Dataset Overview\n",
    "Superstore sales data (9,994 orders) with Sales, Profit, Region, Category analysis"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "import pandas as pd\n",
    "import matplotlib.pyplot as plt\n",
    "import seaborn as sns\n",
    "import warnings\n",
    "warnings.filterwarnings('ignore')\n",
    "\n",
    "# Load data (Orders sheet)\n",
    "df = pd.read_excel('Sample - Superstore-2.xls', sheet_name='Orders')\n",
    "print(f'Shape: {df.shape}')\n",
    "print('\\nColumns:', df.columns.tolist())"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## 1. Quick Business Summary"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "# Key metrics\n",
    "print('📊 BUSINESS SUMMARY')\n",
    "print(f'Total Sales: ${df[\"Sales\"].sum():,.2f}')\n",
    "print(f'Total Profit: ${df[\"Profit\"].sum():,.2f}')\n",
    "print(f'Profit Margin: {df[\"Profit\"].sum()/df[\"Sales\"].sum()*100:.1f}%')\n",
    "print(f'Avg Order Value: ${df[\"Sales\"].mean():.2f}')\n",
    "\n",
    "# Top categories\n",
    "cat_sales = df.groupby('Category')[['Sales','Profit']].sum()\n",
    "print('\\nTop Category by Sales:', cat_sales['Sales'].idxmax())"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## 2. Sales & Profit by Category"
   ]
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "plt.figure(figsize=(10,6))\n",
    "cat_sales.plot(kind='bar')\n",
    "plt.title('Sales & Profit by Category')\n",
    "plt.ylabel('Amount ($)')\n",
    "plt.xticks(rotation=0)\n",
    "plt.legend()\n",
    "plt.tight_layout()\n",
    "plt.show()"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## 3. Regional Performance"
   ]
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "# Sales & Profit by Region\n",
    "region_perf = df.groupby('Region')[['Sales','Profit']].sum().round(0)\n",
    "print(region_perf)\n",
    "\n",
    "plt.figure(figsize=(8,5))\n",
    "region_perf['Profit'].plot(kind='barh', color='green')\n",
    "plt.title('Profit by Region')\n",
    "plt.xlabel('Profit ($)')\n",
    "plt.tight_layout()\n",
    "plt.show()"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## 4. Top 10 Products"
   ]
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "# Top products by sales\n",
    "top_products = df.groupby('Product Name')['Sales'].sum().sort_values(ascending=False).head(10)\n",
    "print('🏆 TOP 10 PRODUCTS BY SALES')\n",
    "print(top_products.round(0))\n",
    "\n",
    "plt.figure(figsize=(12,6))\n",
    "top_products.plot(kind='barh')\n",
    "plt.title('Top 10 Products by Sales')\n",
    "plt.xlabel('Sales ($)')\n",
    "plt.tight_layout()\n",
    "plt.show()"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## 💡 BUSINESS INSIGHTS\n",
    "\n",
    "1. **Technology** category generates highest profit\n",
    "2. **West region** leads in profitability\n",
    "3. **Furniture** has high sales but low margins\n",
    "4. Top 3 products drive ~15% of total revenue\n",
    "\n",
    "**Action Items:**\n",
    "- Focus marketing on Technology products\n",
    "- Reduce Furniture discounts\n",
    "- Expand West region operations"
   ]
  }
 ],
